title: [ONNX][pytorch] Emit Undefined type for value when it is Dynamic type
body_html: For example, outputs of control blocks often have Dynamic type, and when we try to export them to ONNX we get an invalid proto, since elem_type is not populated on the TypeInfoProto. This makes it so at least we can get past the checker, since having a dynamic typed output from a control block should still be semantically valid
